    "body": "I'll admit I've been puzzled by the decision to have objects freed at the end of a block rather than immediately after their last use for precisely these use-cases; the conclusion I came to on this was that it was probably for consistency of performance, as it is probably an expensive thing. I don't have the background to know precisely why it's done this way.\n",
